  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611540/extras/9832efe32abd41d97ee03d142ca6b463.poster.avif?t=1732166765\" width=640 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611540/extras/9832efe32abd41d97ee03d142ca6b463.webm?t=1732166765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611540/extras/9832efe32abd41d97ee03d142ca6b463.mp4?t=1732166765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Magic Frame is an action-packed platformer adventure in which you have to sweat to defeat your enemies. Upgrade your equipment and your own skill to challenge the boss.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Сhallenging levels with many enemies<br></li><li> Kill the boss - these are the only way to go further<br></li><li> Beware of traps<br></li><li> Avoid obstacles<br></li><li> Relive your childhood memories of classic platformers with high quality frame by frame pixel art<br></li><li> Pave your way through a satisfyingly smooth, but challenging platformer</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611540/extras/528b12d022c85f136eed78cffd1713ef.poster.avif?t=1732166765\" width=640 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611540/extras/528b12d022c85f136eed78cffd1713ef.webm?t=1732166765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611540/extras/528b12d022c85f136eed78cffd1713ef.mp4?t=1732166765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611540/extras/9832efe32abd41d97ee03d142ca6b463.poster.avif?t=1732166765\" width=640 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611540/extras/9832efe32abd41d97ee03d142ca6b463.webm?t=1732166765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611540/extras/9832efe32abd41d97ee03d142ca6b463.mp4?t=1732166765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Magic Frame is an action-packed platformer adventure in which you have to sweat to defeat your enemies. Upgrade your equipment and your own skill to challenge the boss.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Сhallenging levels with many enemies<br></li><li> Kill the boss - these are the only way to go further<br></li><li> Beware of traps<br></li><li> Avoid obstacles<br></li><li> Relive your childhood memories of classic platformers with high quality frame by frame pixel art<br></li><li> Pave your way through a satisfyingly smooth, but challenging platformer</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611540/extras/528b12d022c85f136eed78cffd1713ef.poster.avif?t=1732166765\" width=640 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611540/extras/528b12d022c85f136eed78cffd1713ef.webm?t=1732166765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1611540/extras/528b12d022c85f136eed78cffd1713ef.mp4?t=1732166765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
